query:
select to_jsonb(bookmarks.*) as item
            from bookmarks
            where bookmarks.title ilike '%' || $1 || '%'
            and bookmarks.user_id = $2
            union
            select to_jsonb(notes.*) as item
            from notes
            where notes.title ilike '%' || $1 || '%'
            and notes.user_id = $2
            limit 10
